      <task>
        <statement>
          <p>
            Complete <xref ref="tbl-tickets"/> to show the cost of the numbers of movie tickets listed if each ticket costs $8.50.
          </p>
        </statement>
      </task>

      <task>
        <statement>
          <p>
            Plot the data on the graph at right. Label accurate scales for both <m>x</m> and <m>y</m> so that you use most of the graph. Write titles on each axis.
